import React, {useState} from 'react' import WODForm from "./WODForm" function WOD(props) { const {warmUp, strength, workout, coolDown, title, _id} = props const [editToggle, setEditToggle] = useState(false) return (
{!editToggle ? ( <>

{title}

  • {warmUp}
  • {strength}
  • {workout}
  • {coolDown}
) : ( <> )}
) } export default WOD
